        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"498029\">Andreas Hindborg</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/291565-Help/topic/kernel.20Docset.20for.20Dash/near/503950404\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I don’t know what that is. I’m guessing no. Could you put a link?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>It's quite nice offline <a href=\"https://kapeli.com/dash\">docs</a> app (all docs in 1 place)<br>\nTrying to find workaround using rustdoc, without relying on <code>Cargo.toml</code></p>",
