    {
        "content": "<p>I use it for everything. With <a href=\"http://\">cargo-docset</a> I generate docs for any crate easily with <code>cargo-docset docset &amp;&amp; open target/docset/*.docset</code>. And later using Alfred's dash workflow I find anything very easily<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/35136/yqWynJvXZINzBLliwZEG4YOg/image.png\">image.png</a><br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/35136/Xlxhirnz2YuNdd7YGEsLEORd/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/35136/yqWynJvXZINzBLliwZEG4YOg/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"1246x1056\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/35136/yqWynJvXZINzBLliwZEG4YOg/image.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/35136/Xlxhirnz2YuNdd7YGEsLEORd/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"3024x1888\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/35136/Xlxhirnz2YuNdd7YGEsLEORd/image.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
